**Why Netflix?**: They stream 250M hours/day; compression cuts CDN costs (e.g., AWS bills) by 15-25%, reallocating to AI (their rec system uses 100s of GPUs).

**Plan** (Timeline: 3-6 Months):
1. **Research/Outreach (Month 1)**: Analyze Netflix tech stack (HLS/DASH streaming). Contact via LinkedIn (e.g., VP Engineering) with pitch: "2s compression for UHD streams, 20% savings."
2. **Demo/Pilot (Months 2-3)**: Provide custom SDK integration with their AV1 codec. Test on sample streams; show metrics (e.g., "Reduced 7GB/hour to 5.6GB").
